caption: Ordered a 10-piece Wing Meal for dinner. The food was extremely stale, lacked flavor and fries were so soggy they were inedible. Asked for a sweet tea and got a Coke as a replacement - Iced Tea would have been suitable. After some research, this is an extension of Dickeys BBQ - I’d suggest sticking to BBQ and not wings.

Wings are not good. Got the boneless wings half original bbq and half mild buffalo and they were soggy and spongey. Tasted like old cold chicken nuggets in sauce. The fries were also a joke. Gave us like 5 soggy fries (no joke) for $3 something. Won't go back.
